    actionVerbsContext: "Strong action verbs help your bullets land because they make your impact obvious at a glance. Start bullets with verbs like {actionVerbs[0]} or {actionVerbs[1]} and follow immediately with *what* you did, *how* you did it, and *what changed* (time-to-fill, offer acceptance, retention, compliance results).",
    exampleBulletsContext: "These bullets work because they connect keywords to evidence: system used + process owned + measurable outcome. Treat them as patterns and swap in your real scope, constraints, and metrics so the keywords don't feel pasted in.",
